{"id": 3086, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都给自己的工作和生活之间设置了哪些心理上的“分界线”？", "description": "好不好使姑且不论，建立个人生活防火墙的意识还是要有的。（题图来自：iStock ©️ z_wei）", "record_count": 1062, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191210175027RCWkIyTv3LN9XQGx.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-10T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 350466, "content": "跟同事和跟朋友连说话方式都不一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537623}, {"id": 350263, "content": "公司虽然有提供健身房，自己还是在家附近另外办了卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350264, "content": "中午可以点外卖，然而为了走出办公室还是尽量出去吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350265, "content": "懒得给同事分组，社交媒体直接设置两个账号", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350272, "content": "不在微信外的任何社交网络添加同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 243, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 188884}, {"id": 350275, "content": "手机得两个", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311059}, {"id": 350276, "content": "休息日不回复消息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187795}, {"id": 350277, "content": "两个微信，两个qq，两个手机，回家之后工作用手机直接留在公司。", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652793}, {"id": 350278, "content": "虽然很难做到，但尽量不把工作带回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1460782}, {"id": 350279, "content": "还在上大学，学姐对我说:“工作就是去赚钱的，交到真心朋友是万幸，交不到真心朋友才是常态。”好好珍惜最后的纯真美好时光!", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674196}, {"id": 350280, "content": "周五下班切换生活状态，周日临睡前再切回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171698}, {"id": 350281, "content": "休息日就是吃玩睡，绝对不在家处理工作上的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 350282, "content": "上班戴的手环（用来刷公交和公司门禁），在家一定要摘掉，解除封印！", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456035}, {"id": 350283, "content": "在家时工作群@我说工作的事，立马退群！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 350539, "content": "初创业没有分界线", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1274335}, {"id": 350284, "content": "在家时工作群@我说工作的事，立马退群！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603240}, {"id": 352332, "content": "下课不谈学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350286, "content": "放假的时候出门不带表，因为我自己的时间不用赶忙，可以虚耗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1645301}, {"id": 350287, "content": "手机两用，微信两用", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 48640}, {"id": 350289, "content": "QQ上都是好友，微信上全是同事，通常不用微信和朋友圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1668209}, {"id": 350290, "content": "非工作时间，不回复同事任何消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486610}, {"id": 350295, "content": "只是心里划清界限", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 84506}, {"id": 350297, "content": "朋友圈的可见与不可见", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673737}, {"id": 351326, "content": "公事公办，私事私了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560500}, {"id": 351076, "content": "休息绝不做上班活儿😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675471}, {"id": 350333, "content": "穿衣风格\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284224}, {"id": 350337, "content": "下了班就不认识同事了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674337}, {"id": 350346, "content": "不用微信工作，只用邮件，非工作时间一律不回邮件", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 350878, "content": "吃饭时间绝对不碰工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368648}, {"id": 350414, "content": "上班不化妆，周末出去浪才化妆打扮自己！毕竟化妆品也是很贵的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674425}, {"id": 350416, "content": "线上都是任务，线下才是个人时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461775}, {"id": 350708, "content": "又怎能真正分开，难难难", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541038}]}